    "path": "/posts/2021-01-05---scroll-snap-type-i-got-it/scroll-snap-type-i-got-it",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"23192b4e-884b-5a7c-8dd3-3ea02543d619","html":"<p>Today I got a new CSS skill according to the latest CSS tricks newsletter.</p>\n<p>And it is the <code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-type</code>.</p>\n<p>I have to admit that there are no new features can stimulate me after CSS Grid.</p>\n<p>If you havenâ€™t learned it, please visit <a href=\"https://cssgridgarden.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CSS Grid Garden</a>.</p>\n<p>It is so much fun to learn it and use it.</p>\n<p>Despites the dying IE 11 and some mobile browsers, <code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-type</code> is supported in all modern browsers.</p>\n<p>It has two major properties: <code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-type</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-align</code>.</p>\n<p>In order to enable this feature for swiping the entire page.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The parent element needs to define <code class=\"language-text\">overflow:auto | scroll</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">width: 100vw</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">height: 100vh</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-type: x mandatory | y mandatory | x proximity | y proximity</code></li>\n<li>The children define <code class=\"language-text\">width: 100vw</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">height: 100vh</code> as well.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">scroll-snap-align: start | center | end</code> is not required. From my experience, <code class=\"language-text\">start</code> performs more naturally than the others.</p>\n<p>If the child element content is longer than the parent content, <code class=\"language-text\">proximity</code> could allow the user to navigate to the bottom of the content. Then the scrolling effect would work properly.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Element 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Element 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Element 3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Element 4<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-nam